			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character / First person View: Adjust view:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Punch, kick, or action; with back turned against wall, tap on wall:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Crawl, press to duck down. Once ducked, press the Directional Buttons to crawl:                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Enters first person view mode:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Use weapon, throw, or choke:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Punch, kick, or action; with back turned against wall, tap on wall:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Crawl, press to duck down. Once ducked, press the Directional Buttons to crawl:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Item quickchange:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Weapon quickchange:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Equip item:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Equip weapon:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Activate Codec:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
